Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.37,0:00:03.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玄黄端现 太极混沌如鸡蛋\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}ln the beginning, there was darkness...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.87,0:00:05.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随着轰的一声\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and then, bang...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.00,0:00:09.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时间 空间和物质\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}giving birth to an endless expanding existence...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.21,0:00:11.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时间 空间和物质\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}of time, space, and matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.80,0:00:14.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在 所见超乎我们的想象\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Now, see further than we've ever imagined...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.72,0:00:16.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超越了客观认知极限\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}beyond the limits of our existence...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.64,0:00:19.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那地方我们称之为"宇宙"\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}in a place we call "The Universe."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.02,0:00:23.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混沌壮观\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Chaotic and breathtaking...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.73,0:00:27.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们的美丽形成于虚无的空间\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}their beauty forms from the emptiness of space.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.06,0:00:30.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星云是星系的一切 而恒星却不是\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Nebulas are everything in the galaxy that stars are not.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.65,0:00:35.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飘渺的物质 时而聚拢\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Wisps of matter, at times coming together...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.36,0:00:38.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时而散开\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}at others, flying apart...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.58,0:00:41.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朦胧的面纱 翻腾的云团\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}filmy veils, billowing masses...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.58,0:00:45.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有些昏暗 有些闪烁着明亮的色彩\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}some dark, some glowing in brilliant colors...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.79,0:00:50.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,许多形状已见怪不怪\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}many taking the shapes of things that are eerily familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.05,0:00:51.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有趣的是人们看到星云\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt's interesting when people look at nebulas...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.76,0:00:54.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就会开始产生幻觉\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}they sort of start seeing things in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.26,0:00:59.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既非恒星 也非行星 它们才是星系之王\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Neither stars nor planets, they are the crownjewels of the galaxy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.60,0:01:02.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇宙展现了星云里恒星的生死\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The universe reveals its awesome display...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.85,0:01:09.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及创世循环叹为观止的展示\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}of stellar birth, death, and the cycle of creation inside the nebulas.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.15,0:01:13.00,Default,,0,0,1,,{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&H3CF1F3&\b0}--==本影片由 {\1c&HFF8000&\b1}CMCT 团队{\fn华文楷体\1c&H3CF1F3&\b0} 荣誉出品==--\N更多精彩影视 请访问 {\fnCronos Pro Subhead\1c&HFF00FF&\b1}http://cmct.cc{\r}
