Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.00,0:01:22.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[历史频道] 第二季 第十四集 星云\N[History Channel] The UniverseⅡ 14of19 Nebulas
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.33,0:01:26.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是有史以来拍到的最著名的太空照片之一\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt is one of the most famous space photographs ever taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.12,0:01:31.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一如哈勃太空望远镜所见\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}As seen by the Hubble Space Telescope...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.42,0:01:34.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它显示出创造之柱\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}it shows the Pillars of Creation...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.51,0:01:39.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巨大的尘埃和气体柱有7光年之长\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}massive columns of dust and gas seven light-years long.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.80,0:01:43.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们之大 柱子只是其很小一部分\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}As big as they are, the Pillars are just a small part...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.31,0:01:48.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,距离地球6500光年的巨大星际育婴室\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}of an immense stellar nursery 6,500 light-years from Earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.48,0:01:50.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,称为天鹰星云\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}called the Eagle Nebula.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.86,0:01:57.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各种星云散落在繁星之间\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Nebulas of all kinds are scattered among the stars everywhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.20,0:02:02.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我们乃至其它星系间最壮观的景象\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and are among the most spectacular sights...in ours or any galaxy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.49,0:02:05.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星云美丽动人 无一例外\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Nebulae are beautiful, all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.83,0:02:08.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们确实夺人眼球\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}They really strike the eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.71,0:02:13.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根据云的希腊词汇 星云就是\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}From the Greek word for cloud, nebulas are just that...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.50,0:02:18.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星际气体和尘埃的云 肉眼难得一见\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}clouds of interstellar gas and dust, rarely visible to the naked eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.01,0:02:24.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而 通过空间和地面的望远镜\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But with telescopes in space and on Earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.01,0:02:27.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们的美容昭然若揭\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}their beauty is revealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.19,0:02:33.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闪亮 反射或遮掩星系的光辉\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Glowing, reflecting, or obscuring the galaxy's light...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.44,0:02:36.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们是恒星的出生之地\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}they are regions where stars are born...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.15,0:02:39.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丧命之地 爆发之地\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}where stars die, and where explosions...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.90,0:02:43.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是时空结构的刑场\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}rack the very fabric of space-time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.41,0:02:47.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星云的形状千姿百态\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Nebulas have fantastic shapes...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.33,0:02:50.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犹如夏季的云彩\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}like clouds in the sky on a summer day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.21,0:02:55.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们产生的意象往往惟妙惟肖\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}They often evoke imagery that hits very close to home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.71,0:02:57.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似花\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lmages of flowers...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.21,0:03:00.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似虫\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}images of insects...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.39,0:03:04.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似人\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}images of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.10,0:03:07.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有趣的是 人们观察星云时\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt's interesting when people look at nebulas.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.89,0:03:09.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像是做罗沙哈测验(让人解释墨水点绘的图形以判断其性格)\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt's like a Rorschach test.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.56,0:03:12.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们会开始产生幻觉\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}They sort of start seeing things in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.48,0:03:18.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽管 星云都已经贴上了天文学的编目\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Although nebulas are labeled with numbers from astronomical catalogs...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.11,0:03:22.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 好多被创造性地以其位置和形状而冠名\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}many also have names inspired by their locations or shapes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.16,0:03:25.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并不困难 比如\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt's not difficult, for instance...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.91,0:03:30.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来看一下为何这叫做蝴蝶星云\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to see why this is called the Butterfly Nebula...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.41,0:03:33.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这被称为马头星云\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}or this is known as the Horse Head Nebula.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.29,0:03:36.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的例子不胜枚举\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The list goes on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.92,0:03:38.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猎户星云\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The Orion Nebula...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.42,0:03:40.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鬼头星云\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the Ghost Head Nebula...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.17,0:03:41.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刺魟星云\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the Stingray Nebula...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.93,0:03:43.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,旋涡星云\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the Helix Nebula...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.51,0:03:45.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猫眼星云\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the Cat's Eye Nebula...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.09,0:03:46.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,北美星云\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the North American Nebula...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.72,0:03:48.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鹈鹕星云\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the Pelican Nebula.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.60,0:03:53.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星云的千姿百态\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The astonishing forms nebulas take...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.69,0:03:56.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使其成为了星系中的亮丽风景线\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}make them the tourist attractions of the galaxy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.94,0:04:00.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你举家坐上飞碟\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lfyou've got the family in a flying saucer...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.44,0:04:02.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想漂流银河\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and you're careening through the Milky Way...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.28,0:04:06.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想寻找有趣的休憩之处 就去星云吧\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}looking for an interesting rest stop, you're going to go to a nebula.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.00,0:04:13.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宛如地球上的旅游胜地\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Like tourist attractions on Earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.62,0:04:17.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遥远的星云吸引着我们一游为快\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}faraway nebulas entice us for a closer look.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.96,0:04:20.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥们 这是郊游\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Man, it's a hike.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.39,0:04:27.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夜空中最大的诱惑之一\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}One of the prime attractions in the night sky...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.97,0:04:30.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是大猎户星云\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}is the great Orion Nebula...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.31,0:04:35.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你肉眼能看到的极少数星云之一\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}one of the very few nebulas you can see with the naked eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.81,0:04:40.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晴朗之夜 它看上去就像是猎户之剑里的一颗模糊的星星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}On a clear night, it appears as a fuzzy star in the sword of Orion...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.99,0:04:45.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那或许是空中最容易辨认的星座\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}probably the most recognizable constellation in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.82,0:04:49.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猎户星云是银河系里恒星形成最活跃的地区\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The Orion Nebula is the most active area of starformation in our galaxy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.99,0:04:52.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它照亮夜空且别无所求\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt lights up the sky like nothing else.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.16,0:04:53.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以这是个大款\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So this is a big one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.50,0:04:57.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对星云来说这是好莱坞的标记\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}ln terms of nebulas, this is the Hollywood sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.55,0:05:04.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去旅游胜地一游的理由\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And the reason why travelers want to get close to tourist attractions...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.47,0:05:08.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与天文学家仔细观察星云的理由并无二致\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}is the same as why astronomers want a closer look at nebulas.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.39,0:05:11.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家争相举起相机\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}They each want to take photos.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.68,0:05:18.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟是旅游 无论在人间还是天堂\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}After all, tourism, whether earthly or astronomical...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.86,0:05:21.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是到处留影\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}is all about the pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.15,0:05:27.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星云的照片占有非常特殊的地位\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Photographs of nebulas occupy a real special niche...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.28,0:05:29.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常重要的地位 我是这么认为的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}a very important niche, l think...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.41,0:05:34.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为它们真的登峰造极\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}because they really do sit at the pinnacle...
