Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.34,0:24:35.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实现我们人眼无法完成的事情\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}in ways that our eyes cannot do entirely on their own.
