Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.38,0:25:17.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是没办法将星云光谱里的氢与其他元素混淆的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and there's no way to confuse hydrogen...in the spectrum of a nebula with any other element.
