Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.22,0:26:00.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天文学家给了我们另一个观察事物的方法\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}astronomers have given us anotherway of seeing things...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.14,0:26:02.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是我们自己所无法看到的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}we can't see by ourselves.
